author: Precious Reading
text:
'Nepali Nagrik' haru laai 'Nepali Prajaa' banaaune gatibidhi garnu, bolnu vaneko CONSTUTUTION OF REPUBLIC OF NEPAL ko sangeen VOILATION ho. 

'Raajaa ko gaatha gaadi taakdaa' k sajaaya hunnthyo; 'Naagarik ko gaatha gaadi taakdaa' tyahi prakritiko Nagariktantra birodhi, sambidhaan birodhi aparaadha gareko thhahar hunchha ni, kuraa sabaaile bujhhi challnu, bollnu parchha haai.

'Vrasta chaar' ko unmulan garne nagarne sarokaar ko bisaya Naagarik-saktti ko ho.

'Nepali Naagrik' ra Ex RAJTANTRA laai pheri pani judhaaune kaam 'Nepali Prajaa' harule  gariraheko bujhhinchha, tyaso garnu gair-sambaaidhaanic hunchha. Thulo sajaaya ko bhaagidaar ki na hune?

'Nepali-prajaa' vaneko 'Nepali-Naagark' vanndaa pani tallyo darjaa ho ni, 'raaietee' saraha maatra . 

Tyaskaaran le gardaa aafno 'darjaa ghattne'  kaam kunaaipani buddhimaani maanish haru le gardaainan.
